# Keep the build context small: exclude generated/runtime stuff. Docker reads this
# whenever the build context is the workspace root (back/Dockerfile{,.dev}).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.git
**/.DS_Store
**/.vercel
**/.idea
**/.vscode

# App-side artefacts that aren't needed in any image
back/test
back/tests
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
